   "svg_tarjeta": "<svg viewBox='0 0 90 60' fill='none' stroke='#22d3ee' stroke-width='3'><path d='M10 34h70'/><path d='M32 34v-16M58 34v-16'/><path d='M10 34l-6 12h12z'/></svg>",
   "cuestiones": [
    {
     "id": "q2a",
     "titulo": "Pregunta 2.1 (Opción A) · Viga con dos cargas puntuales",
     "etiqueta": "OPCIÓN A",
     "menu": "P2.1 (A) · Viga (2 cargas)",
     "titulo_corto": "P2.1",
     "meta": "2,5 puntos (a: 1,25 · b: 1,25)",
     "enunciado_html": "<p>Para la viga mostrada (P1 = P2 = 800 kg, a = 5 m, L = 12 m):</p><ol type='a'><li>Encuentra las ecuaciones de la fuerza cortante y el momento flector. <span class='pts'>(1,25 puntos)</span></li><li>Dibuja los diagramas correspondientes. <span class='pts'>(1,25 puntos)</span></li></ol>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 640 300' width='100%' style='max-width:580px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif'><line x1='280' y1='60' x2='280' y2='158' stroke='#fb7185' stroke-width='3'/><polygon points='272,146 288,146 280,159' fill='#fb7185'/><text x='280' y='50' fill='#fda4af' font-size='15' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>P1</text><line x1='360' y1='60' x2='360' y2='158' stroke='#fb7185' stroke-width='3'/><polygon points='352,146 368,146 360,159' fill='#fb7185'/><text x='360' y='50' fill='#fda4af' font-size='15' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>P2</text><rect x='80' y='160' width='480' height='15' rx='2' fill='#1e293b' stroke='#e2e8f0' stroke-width='2'/><polygon points='80,175 67,202 93,202' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='67' y1='202' x2='59' y2='212' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><line x1='76' y1='202' x2='68' y2='212' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><line x1='84' y1='202' x2='76' y2='212' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><line x1='93' y1='202' x2='85' y2='212' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='80' y='154' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='15' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>A</text><polygon points='560,175 547,198 573,198' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='553' cy='204' r='5' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='1.8'/><circle cx='567' cy='204' r='5' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='1.8'/><line x1='545' y1='210' x2='575' y2='210' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.6'/><text x='560' y='154' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='15' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>B</text><line x1='80' y1='236' x2='280' y2='236' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><polygon points='80,236 91,231 91,241' fill='#94a3b8'/><polygon points='280,236 269,231 269,241' fill='#94a3b8'/><text x='180' y='227' fill='#cbd5e1' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>a = 5 m</text><line x1='360' y1='236' x2='560' y2='236' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><polygon points='360,236 371,231 371,241' fill='#94a3b8'/><polygon points='560,236 549,231 549,241' fill='#94a3b8'/><text x='460' y='227' fill='#cbd5e1' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>a = 5 m</text><line x1='80' y1='266' x2='560' y2='266' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><polygon points='80,266 91,261 91,271' fill='#94a3b8'/><polygon points='560,266 549,261 549,271' fill='#94a3b8'/><text x='320' y='257' fill='#cbd5e1' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>L = 12 m</text></svg><figcaption>Viga biapoyada de 12 m con dos cargas iguales P1 y P2 situadas a 5 m de cada apoyo.</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>Por simetría (cargas iguales situadas simétricamente) \\(R_A=R_B=\\frac{P_1+P_2}{2}\\). El cortante es constante a tramos y el momento flector es máximo (y constante) en el tramo central entre las cargas.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>Reacciones</h5><div class='formula'>$$R_A=R_B=\\frac{800+800}{2}=800\\,\\mathrm{kg}$$</div><h5>a) Ecuaciones (origen en A)</h5><p>Tramo 0&ndash;5 m: \\(V=800\\,\\mathrm{kg}\\), \\(M=800\\,x\\).</p><p>Tramo 5&ndash;7 m: \\(V=0\\), \\(M=4000\\,\\mathrm{kg\\cdot m}\\) (constante).</p><p>Tramo 7&ndash;12 m: \\(V=-800\\,\\mathrm{kg}\\), \\(M=-800\\,x+9600\\).</p><h5>Valores máximos</h5><div class='formula'>$$V_{max}=800\\,\\mathrm{kg}\\qquad M_{max}=800\\cdot 5=4000\\,\\mathrm{kg\\cdot m}$$</div><div class='res'><b>V<sub>máx</sub> = 800 kg &nbsp;·&nbsp; M<sub>máx</sub> = 4000 kg&middot;m (tramo central)</b></div><h5>b) Diagramas</h5><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 560 300' width='100%' style='max-width:520px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif'><line x1='65' y1='70' x2='530' y2='70' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='65' y='28' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>V (kg)</text><polygon points='70,70 70,36 258,36 258,70' fill='rgba(56,189,248,.18)' stroke='none'/><polygon points='332,70 332,104 520,104 520,70' fill='rgba(251,113,133,.16)' stroke='none'/><polyline points='70,36 258,36 258,70 332,70 332,104 520,104' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.4'/><line x1='70' y1='70' x2='70' y2='36' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.4'/><line x1='520' y1='104' x2='520' y2='70' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.4'/><text x='78' y='30' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='12'>+800</text><text x='512' y='120' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='12' text-anchor='end'>-800</text><line x1='65' y1='240' x2='530' y2='240' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='65' y='148' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>M (kg·m)</text><polygon points='70,240 258,160 332,160 520,240' fill='rgba(74,222,128,.18)' stroke='none'/><polyline points='70,240 258,160 332,160 520,240' fill='none' stroke='#4ade80' stroke-width='2.4'/><text x='295' y='154' fill='#86efac' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>4000</text><text x='70' y='258' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>A</text><text x='520' y='258' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>B</text></svg><figcaption>Cortante escalonado (+800 / 0 / &minus;800 kg) y momento flector trapezoidal (máx. 4000 kg&middot;m).</figcaption></figure>"
    },
