     "titulo_corto": "P3.1",
     "meta": "2,5 puntos (a: 0,75 · b: 0,5 · c: 0,5 · d: 0,75)",
     "enunciado_html": "<p>El circuito equivalente de la bobina de un contactor consta de R = 25 &ohm; y una bobina pura de 45 mH, alimentado a 125 V / 50 Hz. Calcula:</p><ol type='a'><li>Impedancia total. <span class='pts'>(0,75 puntos)</span></li><li>Intensidad total. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Ángulo de desfase. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Caída de tensión en la resistencia y en la bobina. <span class='pts'>(0,75 puntos)</span></li></ol>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 520 250' width='100%' style='max-width:460px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' stroke='#e2e8f0' stroke-width='2.2'><line x1='70' y1='80' x2='238' y2='80'/><line x1='282' y1='80' x2='450' y2='80'/><line x1='70' y1='80' x2='70' y2='200'/><line x1='450' y1='80' x2='450' y2='200'/><line x1='70' y1='200' x2='130' y2='200'/><line x1='250' y1='200' x2='330' y2='200'/><line x1='420' y1='200' x2='450' y2='200'/><circle cx='260' cy='80' r='22' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2.2'/><path d='M246 80 q7 -12 14 0 t14 0' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2'/><text x='260' y='34' fill='#c4b5fd' font-size='15' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>125 V / 50 Hz</text><polyline points='130,200 138,192 154,208 170,192 186,208 202,192 218,208 234,192 242,200 250,200' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.2'/><text x='190' y='236' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>R = 25 &#8486;</text><path d='M330 200 q8 -14 16 0 q8 -14 16 0 q8 -14 16 0 q8 -14 16 0 l6 0' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2.2'/><text x='378' y='236' fill='#fbbf24' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>L = 45 mH</text></svg><figcaption>Circuito RL serie: R = 25 &ohm; y L = 45 mH a 125 V / 50 Hz.</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>\\(X_L=2\\pi f L\\); \\(Z=\\sqrt{R^2+X_L^2}\\); \\(I=\\frac{V}{Z}\\); \\(\\varphi=\\arctan\\frac{X_L}{R}\\); \\(V_R=IR\\), \\(V_L=IX_L\\).</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>a) Impedancia total</h5><div class='formula'>$$X_L=2\\pi\\cdot 50\\cdot 0{,}045=14{,}14\\,\\Omega$$</div><div class='formula'>$$Z=\\sqrt{25^2+14{,}14^2}=\\sqrt{824{,}9}=28{,}72\\,\\Omega$$</div><div class='res'><b>Z &asymp; 28,72 &ohm;</b></div><h5>b) Intensidad total</h5><div class='formula'>$$I=\\frac{125}{28{,}72}=4{,}35\\,\\mathrm{A}$$</div><div class='res'><b>I &asymp; 4,35 A</b></div><h5>c) Ángulo de desfase</h5><div class='formula'>$$\\varphi=\\arctan\\frac{14{,}14}{25}=29{,}5^\\circ$$</div><div class='res'><b>&phi; &asymp; 29,5° (inductivo)</b></div><h5>d) Caídas de tensión</h5><div class='formula'>$$V_R=IR=4{,}35\\cdot 25=108{,}8\\,\\mathrm{V}\\qquad V_L=IX_L=4{,}35\\cdot 14{,}14=61{,}5\\,\\mathrm{V}$$</div><div class='res'><b>V<sub>R</sub> &asymp; 108,8 V &nbsp;·&nbsp; V<sub>L</sub> &asymp; 61,5 V</b></div>"
    },
    {
     "id": "q3b",
     "titulo": "Pregunta 3.2 (Opción B) · Función mayoría con NAND",
     "etiqueta": "OPCIÓN B",
     "menu": "P3.2 (B) · Función mayoría",
     "titulo_corto": "P3.2",
     "meta": "2,5 puntos (a: 0,5 · b: 0,5 · c: 0,5 · d: 1,0)",
     "enunciado_html": "<p>Un motor se controla con tres pulsadores A, B, C y se activa cuando se pulsan <b>al menos dos</b> cualesquiera. Se pide:</p><ol type='a'><li>Tabla de verdad. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Función lógica en primera forma canónica. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Simplificar por Karnaugh. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Implementar con puertas NAND. <span class='pts'>(1 punto)</span></li></ol>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "",
     "aplica_html": "<p>Es la <b>función mayoría</b> de tres variables. La primera forma canónica es la suma de minterms; Karnaugh la reduce y, por De Morgan, la suma de productos se implementa con NAND.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>a) Tabla de verdad</h5><table class='dat'><tr><th>A</th><th>B</th><th>C</th><th>F</th></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr></table><h5>b) Primera forma canónica</h5><div class='formula'>$$F=\\bar ABC+A\\bar BC+AB\\bar C+ABC$$</div><h5>c) Simplificación por Karnaugh</h5><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 440 200' width='100%' style='max-width:410px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif'><text x='96' y='46' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='13'>A\\BC</text><text x='160' y='46' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>00</text><text x='220' y='46' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>01</text><text x='280' y='46' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>11</text><text x='340' y='46' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>10</text><text x='112' y='88' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='130' y='60' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='160' y='89' fill='#64748b' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='190' y='60' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='220' y='89' fill='#64748b' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='250' y='60' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='280' y='89' fill='#4ade80' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='310' y='60' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='340' y='89' fill='#64748b' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><text x='112' y='134' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='130' y='106' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='160' y='135' fill='#64748b' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='190' y='106' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='220' y='135' fill='#4ade80' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='250' y='106' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='280' y='135' fill='#4ade80' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='310' y='106' width='60' height='46' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='340' y='135' fill='#4ade80' font-size='18' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='246' y='102' width='128' height='54' rx='9' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2.2'/><rect x='184' y='98' width='132' height='62' rx='12' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.2'/><rect x='242' y='54' width='76' height='104' rx='11' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2.2'/></svg><figcaption>Grupos AB (naranja), AC (azul) y BC (violeta).</figcaption></figure><div class='formula'>$$F=AB+AC+BC$$</div><div class='res'><b>F = AB + AC + BC</b></div><h5>d) Implementación con NAND</h5><p>\\(F=\\overline{\\overline{AB}\\cdot\\overline{AC}\\cdot\\overline{BC}}\\): tres NAND de 2 entradas y una NAND de 3 entradas.</p><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 470 260' width='100%' style='max-width:440px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' stroke='#e2e8f0' stroke-width='1.8'><path d='M120 20 L142.0 20 A22.0 22.0 0 0 1 142.0 64 L120 64 Z' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='169.0' cy='42.0' r='4.5' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M120 95 L142.0 95 A22.0 22.0 0 0 1 142.0 139 L120 139 Z' fill='none' stroke='#34d399' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='169.0' cy='117.0' r='4.5' fill='none' stroke='#34d399' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M120 170 L142.0 170 A22.0 22.0 0 0 1 142.0 214 L120 214 Z' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='169.0' cy='192.0' r='4.5' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2'/><text x='95' y='30' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>A</text><text x='95' y='52' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>B</text><text x='95' y='105' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>A</text><text x='95' y='127' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>C</text><text x='95' y='180' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>B</text><text x='95' y='202' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>C</text><line x1='108' y1='30' x2='120' y2='30'/><line x1='108' y1='50' x2='120' y2='50'/><line x1='108' y1='105' x2='120' y2='105'/><line x1='108' y1='125' x2='120' y2='125'/><line x1='108' y1='180' x2='120' y2='180'/><line x1='108' y1='200' x2='120' y2='200'/><path d='M320 95 L335.0 95 A35.0 35.0 0 0 1 335.0 165 L320 165 Z' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='375.0' cy='130.0' r='4.5' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='177' y1='42' x2='250' y2='42'/><line x1='250' y1='42' x2='250' y2='108'/><line x1='250' y1='108' x2='320' y2='108'/><line x1='177' y1='117' x2='250' y2='117'/><line x1='250' y1='117' x2='250' y2='125'/><line x1='250' y1='125' x2='320' y2='125'/><line x1='177' y1='192' x2='250' y2='192'/><line x1='250' y1='192' x2='250' y2='142'/><line x1='250' y1='142' x2='320' y2='142'/><line x1='383' y1='130' x2='450' y2='130'/><text x='456' y='135' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15'>F</text></svg><figcaption>Implementación de la función mayoría con puertas NAND.</figcaption></figure>"
    }
