   "cuestiones": [
    {
     "id": "q4a",
     "titulo": "Pregunta 4.1 (Opción A) · Función de transferencia Z = f(X)",
     "etiqueta": "OPCIÓN A",
     "menu": "P4.1 (A) · Diagrama de bloques",
     "titulo_corto": "P4.1",
     "meta": "2,5 puntos",
     "enunciado_html": "<p>Dado el diagrama de bloques de la figura, obtén la función de transferencia \\(Z=f(X)\\). <span class='pts'>(2,5 puntos)</span></p>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 880 340' width='100%' style='max-width:800px;height:auto' fill='none' stroke='#cbd5e1' stroke-width='2' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' font-size='14'><defs><marker id='ar' markerWidth='9' markerHeight='8' refX='7' refY='3' orient='auto'><path d='M0,0 L7,3 L0,6 Z' fill='#cbd5e1'/></marker></defs><line x1='60' y1='150' x2='118' y2='150' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='134' cy='150' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='124' y1='140' x2='144' y2='160' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='144' y1='140' x2='124' y2='160' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='150' y1='150' x2='300' y2='150' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='300' y='128' width='82' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='341.0' y='155.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P1</text><line x1='382' y1='150' x2='560' y2='150' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='576' cy='150' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='566' y1='140' x2='586' y2='160' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='586' y1='140' x2='566' y2='160' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='592' y1='150' x2='760' y2='150' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><text x='34' y='155' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>X</text><text x='772' y='155' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>Z</text><circle cx='95' cy='150' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><circle cx='470' cy='150' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><text x='116' y='136' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='120' y='176' fill='#fb7185' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>−</text><text x='560' y='136' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='564' y='176' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><rect x='480' y='250' width='82' height='40' rx='5' stroke='#a78bfa'/><text x='521.0' y='275.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P3</text><rect x='300' y='250' width='82' height='40' rx='5' stroke='#a78bfa'/><text x='341.0' y='275.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P2</text><line x1='470' y1='150' x2='470' y2='270' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='470' y1='270' x2='562' y2='270' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='480' y1='270' x2='382' y2='270' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='300' y1='270' x2='134' y2='270' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='134' y1='270' x2='134' y2='168' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='95' y1='150' x2='95' y2='315' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='95' y1='315' x2='576' y2='315' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='576' y1='315' x2='576' y2='168' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/></svg><figcaption>Lazo interno de G<sub>1</sub>... con realimentación P<sub>2</sub>·P<sub>3</sub> (negativa) y una rama directa de X que se suma a la salida.</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>El lazo de \\(P_1\\) realimentado por \\(P_2P_3\\) (negativo) da \\(\\frac{P_1}{1+P_1P_2P_3}\\). Además, la entrada \\(X\\) se suma directamente a la salida en el segundo comparador.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>Lazo interno</h5><p>Sea \\(Y\\) la señal tras \\(P_1\\). El primer comparador da \\(X-P_2P_3\\,Y\\), luego \\(Y=P_1(X-P_2P_3Y)\\):</p><div class='formula'>$$Y=\\frac{P_1}{1+P_1P_2P_3}\\,X$$</div><h5>Salida (segundo comparador: Y + X)</h5><div class='formula'>$$Z=Y+X=\\left(\\frac{P_1}{1+P_1P_2P_3}+1\\right)X$$</div><div class='formula'>$$\\boxed{\\dfrac{Z}{X}=\\dfrac{1+P_1+P_1P_2P_3}{1+P_1P_2P_3}}$$</div><div class='res'><b>Z/X = (1 + P<sub>1</sub> + P<sub>1</sub>P<sub>2</sub>P<sub>3</sub>) / (1 + P<sub>1</sub>P<sub>2</sub>P<sub>3</sub>)</b></div>"
    },
