     "enunciado_html": "<p>Simplifica el siguiente sistema de control hasta conseguir la función de transferencia. <span class='pts'>(2,5 puntos)</span></p>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 880 340' width='100%' style='max-width:800px;height:auto' fill='none' stroke='#cbd5e1' stroke-width='2' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' font-size='14'><defs><marker id='ar' markerWidth='9' markerHeight='8' refX='7' refY='3' orient='auto'><path d='M0,0 L7,3 L0,6 Z' fill='#cbd5e1'/></marker></defs><line x1='70' y1='160' x2='108' y2='160' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='110' y='138' width='82' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='151.0' y='165.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>G1</text><line x1='192' y1='160' x2='252' y2='160' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='268' cy='160' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='258' y1='150' x2='278' y2='170' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='278' y1='150' x2='258' y2='170' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='284' y1='160' x2='340' y2='160' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='342' y='138' width='82' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='383.0' y='165.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>G2</text><line x1='424' y1='160' x2='486' y2='160' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='502' cy='160' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='492' y1='150' x2='512' y2='170' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='512' y1='150' x2='492' y2='170' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='518' y1='160' x2='574' y2='160' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='576' y='138' width='82' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='617.0' y='165.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>G3</text><line x1='658' y1='160' x2='800' y2='160' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><text x='40' y='165' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='start'>E(s)</text><text x='812' y='165' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='start'>C(s)</text><rect x='305' y='62' width='82' height='40' rx='5' stroke='#a78bfa'/><text x='346.0' y='87.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>H2</text><circle cx='460' cy='160' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><line x1='460' y1='160' x2='460' y2='82' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='460' y1='82' x2='387' y2='82' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='305' y1='82' x2='268' y2='82' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='268' y1='82' x2='268' y2='142' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><text x='285' y='96' fill='#4ade80' font-size='15' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='250' y='184' fill='#4ade80' font-size='15' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='486' y='144' fill='#4ade80' font-size='15' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='512' y='194' fill='#fb7185' font-size='17' text-anchor='start'>−</text><circle cx='88' cy='160' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><line x1='88' y1='160' x2='88' y2='300' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='88' y1='300' x2='502' y2='300' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='502' y1='300' x2='502' y2='178' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/></svg><figcaption>Lazo interno de G<sub>2</sub> con H<sub>2</sub> (positivo) y lazo externo unitario negativo tomado de la línea de entrada.</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>El lazo positivo de \\(G_2\\) con \\(H_2\\) da \\(\\frac{G_2}{1-G_2H_2}\\). La rama inferior resta la propia entrada \\(E\\) en el segundo comparador.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>Lazo interno (H<sub>2</sub>, positivo)</h5><div class='formula'>$$G_2'=\\frac{G_2}{1-G_2H_2}$$</div><h5>Camino directo y comparador final</h5><p>Al segundo comparador llega \\(G_1G_2'\\,E\\) por arriba y se resta \\(E\\) por abajo; tras \\(G_3\\):</p><div class='formula'>$$\\boxed{\\dfrac{C(s)}{E(s)}=G_3\\left(\\dfrac{G_1G_2}{1-G_2H_2}-1\\right)=\\dfrac{G_3\\,(G_1G_2-1+G_2H_2)}{1-G_2H_2}}$$</div><div class='res'><b>C/E = G<sub>3</sub>(G<sub>1</sub>G<sub>2</sub> − 1 + G<sub>2</sub>H<sub>2</sub>) / (1 − G<sub>2</sub>H<sub>2</sub>)</b></div>"
